<font color="red">Requires CS:S and Gungame Mod for play.</font>

Installation instructions, getting started tips, and documentation:
 <font color="red">Install the .bsp into your C:/program files/steam/steamapps/(username)/counterstrike source/cstrike/maps. To play the map, Start CS:S and click create server. From the drop down list select gg_stampede and click start.</font>
